BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 663.00 Tm (INSERT, it throws an exception. Match the method to the SQL verb. And there is a bonus in that) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 648.00 Tm (row count - it tells you whether anything actually changed. An UPDATE on an id that does not) Tj ET
